Thank you for downloading Isilex.

First step:
-----------

If you already hava java, you can start Isilex by double-clicking on Isilex.jar. 

You can download an embedded java IsilexlLght solution. You will find a bash script file
in you IsilexRight Root Directory.

If your computer shows Security alerts, trust IsilexLigh.

IsilexLight will display a little green icon near your system Tray.

IsilexLight is ready for working.

Work on:
--------

IsilexLight is now available at http://localhost:8984.

Other computers can reach your project computer. On your network, or on the web, if you
already have a private domain name, IsilexLight is reachable at:

- http://mondomaine.ip:8984

CoWorkers can connect and collaborate. 

If you're running a firewall, don't forget toopen UP/DOWN UDP/TCP on port: 8984 and 8985.
